{"type": "article", "id": 3365, "title": "电视台用上了微软送的 iPad 支架，叫 Surface", "description": "做植入广告，不只是把东西送过去这么简单。", "date": "2014-11-10T08:35:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 260, "name": "微软"}, {"id": 3746, "name": "Surface"}, {"id": 382, "name": "iPad"}, {"id": 4056, "name": "Surface Pro"}], "category": 4, "author": 3, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607171400DUqxXuzk3LSnhVOY.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">为了提高</span><span class=\"s2\"> Surface Pro </span><span class=\"s1\">的出镜频率，微软和</span><span class=\"s2\"> CNN </span><span class=\"s1\">合作提供了一批</span><span class=\"s2\"> Surface Pro 3 </span><span class=\"s1\">给</span><span class=\"s2\"> CNN </span><span class=\"s1\">评论员和主持人使用。这个举措也获得了一批</span><span class=\"s2\"> Twitter </span><span class=\"s1\">用户的支持，有人表示自己是因为</span><span class=\"s2\"> Surface Pro 3 </span><span class=\"s1\">才看</span><span class=\"s2\"> CNN </span><span class=\"s1\">的。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s2\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s2\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s2\">不过情况似乎并不像微软预想的那样，最近有位</span><span class=\"s3\"> CNN </span><span class=\"s2\">主持人还是在</span><span class=\"s3\"> Surface Pro 3 </span><span class=\"s2\">背后悄悄使用</span><span class=\"s3\"> iPad：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s2\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607171359YbUBq8HPXpmac3lG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.81875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s2\">甚至还有评论员将</span><span class=\"s3\"> Surface Pro 3 </span><span class=\"s2\">作为</span><span class=\"s3\"> iPad </span><span class=\"s2\">支架。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s2\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s2\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">不过事后这位</span><span class=\"s2\"> CNN </span><span class=\"s1\">评论员</span><span class=\"s2\"> Jake Tapper </span><span class=\"s1\">也在自己的</span><span class=\"s2\"> Twitter </span><span class=\"s1\">上做出了<a href=\"https://twitter.com/jaketapper/status/530187393869950977\"><span class=\"s4\">回应</span></a>，表示照片中的他正在用</span><span class=\"s2\"> iPad </span><span class=\"s1\">刷</span><span class=\"s2\"> Twitter </span><span class=\"s1\">消息，同时他也在用</span><span class=\"s2\"> Surface Pro 3 </span><span class=\"s1\">查看股票数据。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s2\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s2\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s2\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s2\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s2\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">这不是</span><span class=\"s2\"> Surface Pro </span><span class=\"s1\">第一次被合作方的</span><span class=\"s2\"> iPad </span><span class=\"s1\">砸场子了。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s2\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s2\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s2\">在今年</span><span class=\"s3\"> 9 </span><span class=\"s2\">月，微软花了</span><span class=\"s3\">4 </span><span class=\"s2\">亿美元的</span><span class=\"s3\"> NFL </span><span class=\"s2\">广告投放让</span><span class=\"s3\"> Surface </span><span class=\"s2\">成为“</span><span class=\"s3\">NFL </span><span class=\"s2\">赛事官方使用平板”，在比赛过程中一位解说员将</span><span class=\"s3\"> Surface </span><span class=\"s2\">认成了</span><span class=\"s3\"> iPad</span><span class=\"s2\">，而另一位是将</span><span class=\"s3\"> Surface </span><span class=\"s2\">描述成“类似</span><span class=\"s3\"> iPad </span><span class=\"s2\">的工具”。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s2\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s2\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s2\">看起来微软在</span><span class=\"s3\"> Surface Pro </span><span class=\"s2\">广告上除了砸钱，还得继续加强培训。</span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}